race.description: Brother C V Bell Mdn Hcp
race.comment: Tricky and the betting will be instructive. WAEREA (1) missed a nose here on debut and has been well trialled. Maps well and he can go one better with the extra fitness. SWING STATE (6) resumed in the same race and didn't have much luck. He will have taken fitness and learning and can be a player today. SUPER SCOTCH (3), TORMANZOR (4) and SAVVY SPY (2) are all debutants from leading metro yards. No standout trials from them, but the first pair map well and the market moves should tell the story with these newcomers. KUWAIT (8) is racing well and it wouldn't surprise if he found a place at least.
